title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J. Kaiser Convention Center on 1986-12-31
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw-> Sugaree, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Candyman, Desolation Row, U.S. Blues

Set 2

Touch Of Gray-> Let It Grow, Black Muddy River-> Samson & Delilah, Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Wharf Rat-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Turn On Your Love Light

Set 3

Gimme Some Lovin'-> When Push Comes To Shove, Box Of Rain, In The Midnight Hour-> Brokedown Palace

FM Broadcast on KFOG

David Crosby then The Neville Brothers opened
